                    overlayDescription="A cancer diagnosis can impact family finances, from taking time off work to housing and transportation. Our nonprofit partner Family Reach answers the call, and now they’re expanding to help even more families with a $5 million gift from AbbVie. Watch how they’re creating an impact."
                    overlayHeading="Navigating the hidden side of cancer"
